      <title>Wipro 执行主席 Rishad Premji 谈特朗普支持增长和移民的议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-22/rishad-premji-on-trump-pro-growth-immigration-agenda-video</link>
